      <title>韩国前贸易部长称尹永哲犯下严重错误</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/yoon-made-grave-mistake-says-former-south-korean-trade-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国前贸易部长批评总统尹锡烈颁布戒严令的错误决定，该决定引发了公众的强烈抗议并震动了全球金融市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/yoon-made-grave-mistake-says-former-south-korean-trade-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 07:39:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
